Grimmler/Smokescreen:



Smokescreen watched Bright Blade, looking around a little dumbfounded, a 
shiver going up his spine.  She was rather cold, but he had noticed that the 
water was disappearing, and the sprinkler systems and foam systems were going 
off.  

---

Grimmler shook his head, walking towards Bright Blade, stopping a few feet 
away from her, shaking his head slightly, trying to figure out why he 
suddenly felt he was in love with that Predacon, when he had never met her 
before in his life!

-I have to keep my head together- he said in his mind, taking another step 
towards Bright Blade.
